Package com.sri.ai.util.ml.decisiontree.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DecisionTree<V,L>
    A decision tree from feature vectors of type V, with features of type F, and labels of type L.
    DecisionTreeFactory<V,L>
    A decision tree factory.
    DecisionTreeLearner<V,L>
    A function mapping collections of data to a learned decision tree.
    SplitAnalysis<V,L>  
    SplitAnalyzer<V,L>
    An interface for classes providing a split analysis given a data collection.
